\subsection{Relative dimension}
\begin{definition}\label{cmf.relative_dimension}
\uses{cmf.newform}
The **relative dimension** of a {{KNOWL('cmf.newform', 'newform')}} in a space of modular forms $S_k^{\mathrm{new}}(\Gamma_0(N),\chi)$ is the dimension of its coefficient field as an extension of the character field $\Q(\chi)$ (the number field generated by the values of $\chi$).
\end{definition}


